Historical Closure Data 1998 - 2022

Closures

  1. 2011 - Results impacted by Hurricane Irene (last week of beach season)
  2. 2017 - Results impacted by change in sampling protocol
    (samples collected Thursday/Friday led to an increase in weekend closures)
  3. 2020 - Results impacted by COVID-19
    (inland beaches not sampled until 7/14/20, 7 inland beaches remained closed due to COVID-19 policy)
  4. 2021 - Mashamoquet Brook swimming area closed for entire 2021 season and not sampled
  5. 2022 - Mashamoquet Brook swimming area closed for entire 2022 season and not sampled
